T*
(8. Summary) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In its current form, the repository does what Assignment 4 is supposed to establish. It) Tj
T*
(separates code, configuration, data, outputs, and documentation; it provides one repeatable) Tj
T*
(way to run preprocessing and training from the bundled sample inputs; and it leaves behind) Tj
T*
(enough metadata to connect results to a specific configuration and code state.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The sample data are intentionally small and synthetic, but the technical foundation is now) Tj
T*
(clear, runnable, and ready for the next stage of the work.) Tj
ET
